title: Match facts: Barcelona v Eibar (Spain La Liga)
text:

Eibar: Asier Riesgo, Aleksandar Pantic, Ander Capa, Mauro Dos Santos, David Junca, Simone Verdi (Sergi Enrich 54), Gonzalo Escalante, Takashi Inui (Perez 81), Dani Garcia (Eddy Israfilov 46), Keko. Borja Baston

Barcelona: 3rd, 18 pts, 8 matches,6 win, 0 draw, 2 loss
Eibar: 6th, 13pts, 8 matches, 3 wins, 4 draw, 1 loss
